data.item-format#Item Format:
Each item in the items array follows this format:
{ weight, { name = 'item_name', amount = 1, metadata = {}, rarity = 'optional' } }
Property	Type	Required	Description	weight	number	Yes	Drop weight (higher = more common)	name	string	Yes	Item name to give to player	amount	number	Yes	Quantity of item to give	metadata	table	No	Custom metadata to attach to item	rarity	string	No	Override auto-calculated rarity

